        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">We use <text styleclass="VariableName">CopyMinder® </text>for our software protection.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">When you buy <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">MechDesigner</text>, we email you a <text styleclass="VariableName">Product Key. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">You need the <text styleclass="VariableName">Product-Key</text> to run <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">MechDesigner</text> the first time, or to move MechDesigner to a different computer.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">If you have a <text styleclass="VariableName">Network-License</text> (also called a <text styleclass="VariableName">Floating-License</text>), your <text style="font-style:normal;">I.T. </text>department should install <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">MechDesigner. </text>I.T. should keep the <text styleclass="VariableName">Product Key</text>. </para>
